## Security Checklist

> Full details: [docs/security-checklist.md.template](docs/security-checklist.md.template)

Every PR must verify:

1. **Authentication & Authorization** — Endpoint access control verified
2. **Input Validation** — SQL/NoSQL/external input properly escaped
3. **Data Exposure** — No sensitive data in logs or responses
4. **Infrastructure Isolation** — Internal service ports not exposed
5. **Dependency Vulnerabilities** — External library CVEs checked

